file.name: simpleSchemaWithOuterPropertiesSpec.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.1.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.swagger.io/v1
paths:
  /test:
    post:
      summary: schema with outer properties
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:    
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/schema1"
              required:
                - notRequiredElement
      responses:
        default:
          description: ok
components:
  schemas:
    schema1:
      type: 
        - object
      required:
        - objectType
      properties:
        objectType:
          type: 
            - integer
            - string
        notRequiredElement:
          type:
            - string

Error: callback: json: cannot unmarshal array into Go struct field Schema.type of type string
